data.description: Sellers moved and need to get this one off the books. Custom built 3124 Sq. Ft. home with Lake Hudson views in a quiet neighborhood situated on a dead end road. There is plenty of room to live, work, play & entertain here. Split floorplan with 3 bedroom 2 full & 2 half baths and home office. Large living area w hardwood floors, towering ceiling and fireplace. Extend living to outdoors poolside under the covered patio. Enormous kitchen and dining area with breakfast bar, granite countertops and stainless appliances. Primary bedroom w/ ensuite bath, oversized marble shower and massive walk in closet with natural lighting. Home office or media room. Multi purpose upstairs flex room. Private entry from the primary suite to the enclosed poolside patio. Inground gunite beach entry pool. 3 Car side entry garage. Whole house back up generator. Short drive to several free options for public launch on Lake Hudson. Ask your agent for details on the nearby 2.22 acres with water access available for an additional price. Schedule an appointment today and lets get you Home Sweet Home for the Holidays.
